        "subject": "LU-XXXX o2iblnd: Add histograms in /proc",
        "message": "LU-XXXX o2iblnd: Add histograms in /proc\n\nThis change is intended to increase visibility into the o2iblnd layer by\nexporting certain information to /proc. Two histograms are exported by\nthis change.\n\nThe first shows the time spent on the ibc_active_txs queue by transmit\npackets. This tells us how long it took the IB layer to actually send a\nmessage once Lustre handed it off.\n\nThe second shows the time that the kib_conn_t sat on the kib_sched_list\nqueue.\n\nSigned-off-by: Christopher J. Morrone <morrone2@llnl.gov>\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I97f18616aab7c06b0bdf76010960d0c00b2ab5d3\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
